OL,5, A Virginia school teacher who was shot 
OL,6, by her six-year-old student has filed a
OL,7, $40m (#32m) lawsuit against school     
OL,8, officials, alleging gross negligence   
OL,9, for ignoring warning signs.            
OL,11,FThe lawsuit, filed on Monday, argues   
OL,12,Fthe defendants knew the child "had a   
OL,13,Fhistory of random violence".           
OL,15,FAbigail 'Abby' Zwerner, 25, was shot on
OL,16,F6 January in the hand and upper chest  
OL,17,Fand spent two weeks in hospital.       
OL,19,FShe has undergone four surgeries.      
